        "@type": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string",
        "@value": "Watch for low health literacy cues: excessive nodding, no questions asked, avoidance of written materials, inability to restate information; simplify language to a 6th-grade level; use pictograms or visual aids where available; apply teach-back proactively."
      }
